The phrase "Servant Leader" is commonly used to distinguish the behavior of an effective Agile leader from that of a [[Project Manager]]. The basics are described succinctly in [[The Agile Tao|https://leanpub.com/agiletao/read#leanpub-auto-a-captain]]. The key to playing a Servant Leader role in XSCALE is assuring the [[Fire Keepers' Unanimity]].
